title: Morning Joe 4/2/21
description: A DOJ investigation into Rep. Matt Gaetz, R-Fla., and an indicted Florida politician is focusing on their involvement with multiple women who were recruited online for sex and received cash payments, according to reports. Michael Schmidt discusses.
